      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint condition. The exterior paint and body are flawless with no scratches, dents, or chips. The interior is in pristine condition, showing no signs of wear on the upholstery or carpets. It is mechanically perfect and has been maintained to the highest standard.",
